@lynxy wrote:

The cache File is Bascially a File with All the Things needed to run a Applet. call it a CD if you wish, its like playing a PC game with a CD the CD operates as Storage for the Game, and becase servers come with no “CD” they make a Cache this is Editted / My Computer / Programs :C drive then it should be there. Depending on your OS.

Hope this helped
